bitenum.description: The CLKX, FSX, DX, and CLKS pins are serial port pins.
If XRST = 0, the CLKX, FSX, and DX pins are GPIO pins. The CLKS is also a GPIO pin if RRST = 0 and RIOEN = 1.

bitenum.description: The CLKR, FSR, DR, and CLKS pins are serial port pins.
If RRST = 0, the CLKR, FSR, and DR pins are GPIO pins. The CLKS is also a GPIO pin if XRST = 0 and XIOEN = 1.
Transmit frame synchronization is supplied by an external source via the FSX pin.

Receive frame synchronization is supplied by an external source via the FSR pin.
Receive frame synchronization is supplied by the sample rate generator FSR is an output pin reflecting internal FSR, except when GSYNC = 1 in SRGR2.
